险呈现显著稳定正相关关系。可见特质流动性风险作为一个区别于其他特征变量的单独变量作用于资产定价。</p><table-wrap-group id="3"><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table3">Table 3</xref></label><caption><title> (a) Portfolios based on double-variables (SIZE, BM, TURN); (b) Portfolios based on double-variables (RET12M, ILLIQ, IVOL</title></caption><table-wrap id="3_1"><caption><title> (b)</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="2"  ></th><th align="center" valign="middle"  colspan="3"  >SIZE</th><th align="center" valign="middle"  colspan="3"  >BM</th><th align="center" valign="middle"  colspan="4"  >TURN</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >S1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >S2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >S3</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >BM1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >BM2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >BM3</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >T1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >T2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >T3</td><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >P1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >−0.0031</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >−0.0034</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.0029</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.0092</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >−0.0022</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >−0.0072</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >−0.0031</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >−0.0031</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.0049</td><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >P2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.0046</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.0102</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.0167</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.0287</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.0071</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.0005</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.0042</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.